Create the drop-in ini:

cat >/usr/local/etc/php/conf.d/zz-logging.ini <<'EOF'
log_errors = On
error_reporting = E_ALL
display_errors = Off
error_log = /var/www/html/dev1/apis/php-error.log
EOF

--------------

Make sure the path exists and is writable by PHPâ€™s user (often www-data):

mkdir -p /var/www/html/dev1/apis
touch /var/www/html/dev1/apis/php-error.log
chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/dev1/apis
chmod -R 775 /var/www/html/dev1/apis